text:
Does anyone know what the IP Range or Source Location would be for HubSpot SEO Scan traffic?
We are seeing a spike in traffic from yesterday, and I did kick off an SEO Scan of the website.

However, the X-Header is not returning to include “X-HubSpot-Signature”.

Our Cloudflare shows the spike as “Machine Learning”, with most IPs being in range 54.174.58.235-248.
